{"tid":1822350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！伊拉克空軍基地遭多枚火箭炮攻擊　4軍人受傷","createTime":"2020-01-13T02:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T02:50:25.000Z","uid":91914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"443dfe5a70b6478f9ec8c5137a57974c5cc7262f","tid":1822350,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"伊拉克軍方1月12日表示，首都巴格達北部的拜萊德空軍基地（Balad Air Base）遭多枚火箭炮攻擊，造成4名伊拉克軍人受傷。<br />\n軍方聲明指出，8枚卡短程喀秋莎（Katyusha）火箭炮降落在拜萊德空軍基地炸傷2名伊拉克軍官和2名空軍士兵。<br />\n<br />\n法新社引述兩名軍方消息人士指，曾有一批美國空軍特遣部隊和承包商駐守在拜萊德空軍基地，但由於近兩周美國與伊朗關係緊張，大部分美方人員已經撤走。其中一名消息人士指，該基地內最多只有15名美軍官兵和1架飛機。<br />\n<br />\n日前美軍在伊拉克的兩個空軍基地遭伊朗發射火箭炮攻擊，被指是報復美軍殺死伊朗商級指揮官的行動，並一度令美伊關係急劇緊張。惟美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）發表全國講話，強調無意對伊朗動用軍事力量，令事件得以降溫。<br />\n<br />\n暫時只搵到01，唔比link了"},{"pid":"8a64594bc78ed54aa9fa9f3f76bbeffd2bc2e281","tid":1822350,"uid":65952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bef31c79316f3a5b1b2a657e7c148afe457fef","tid":1822350,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dc9c2c47e248b54c265e1d91adf0aee426dd37","tid":1822350,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:22:59.000Z","msg":"好嘢<br />\n逆轉伊拉克民意來反伊朗"},{"pid":"8643880dfa40b82e6683cc62c24ce856e5c0cdac","tid":1822350,"uid":274330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"0 -0"},{"pid":"f6ef49cc5c7dea1f112bbb8cf96ba2269efb69b5","tid":1822350,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT